    <data key="d0">Samsung Cloud Global Architecture with Transit Gateway</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K5ww_O4vsxo</data>
    <data key="d2">Samsung Cloud provides backup and restore services for Galaxy smartphone users globally (Korea, US, Europe, China, Singapore). The primary design challenge was securing and managing high volumes of inter-region data traffic for hundreds of millions of users. AWS Transit Gateway was adopted to create a single, simplified, and secure private network across multiple AWS regions, replacing public network communication for inter-region traffic. The architecture also plans to integrate on-premises data centers via Direct Connect Gateway and other services via Site-to-Site VPN into this unified private network.</data>
    <data key="d3">data_ingestion, interactive, compute_intensive, control</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
